  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Phaser</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>A large flightless bipedal avian race, <span class=
=3DSpellE>Banoserit</span>
  have short legs and exceptionally large hands on long arms. Covered in
  feathers the <span class=3DSpellE>Banoserit</span> are rarely seen withou=
t most
  of the body covered in clothing.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Banoserit</span> are a depe=
ndable
  species who hold themselves and others to high moral values. Reputation is
  exceptionally important to them.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>To be a <span class=3DSpellE>Banoserit</span> is to =
accept
  total responsibility for your own sins and the sins of your ancestors. Th=
ey
  believe that if an individual&#8217;s ancestors did something morally bad
  that this behavior is in their blood and they will accept the merciless
  judgement of their own species.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Banoserit</span> are gifted=
 with
  the most exceptional eyes of all known species. This is because a large p=
art
  of their brain processes sensory input.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Banoserit</span> spend grea=
t effort
  to attempt to unlock this ability further for use in scanning the 'skies'=
 of
  space as an early warning system of danger.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>This has led to the development of the Far Sight Cen=
ter,
  considerably more effective than most Long-Range Scanners.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Banoserit</span> are found =
in
  large, unusually vertical cities in the deserts of the driest planets.</p>
